---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Team - Chasers DD Luxury Service"
  description="Meet the professional team behind Chasers DD premium designated driver service. Experienced drivers and dedicated support staff committed to luxury transportation."
  keywords="team, professional drivers, luxury transportation staff, Chasers DD team, Arizona designated drivers"
>
  <Navigation />

  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-gray-900 to-black">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-2 sm:px-3 lg:px-4">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          <span class="font-serif">Our</span>
          <span class="text-[#c69214] ml-3">Team</span>
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        >
          Meet the dedicated professionals who make luxury transportation
          exceptional. Our experienced team is committed to providing unmatched
          service and peace of mind.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Story Section -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-2 sm:px-3 lg:px-4 pb-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          At Chasers Designated Drivers, our team is the driving force behind
          everything we do.
        </p>

        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#c69214]/20 to-[#b8841c]/20 border border-[#c69214]/30 rounded-xl p-8 mb-12"
        >
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Founded in 2010 by Vincent Rocky Medina, Chasers was built on one
            simple mission:
          </p>
          <blockquote class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#c69214] mb-4 font-serif">
            "We just need to be successful one call at a time."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            That mindset continues to guide us today—ride after ride, night
            after night.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Team Members Section -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <!-- Team Member 1 -->
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-800 to-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700 text-center animate-on-scroll"
        >
          <div
            class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#c69214] to-[#b8841c] rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-12 h-12 text-black"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-serif">Rocky</h3>
          <p class="text-[#c69214] font-medium mb-4">Founder & Lead Driver</p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            With over a decade of experience in luxury transportation, Rocky
            founded Chasers DD to provide unmatched professional service and
            peace of mind for every client.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-left max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            What sets us apart isn't just our commitment to safety—it's the
            people behind the wheel and behind the scenes. Our drivers,
            dispatchers, and support staff are united by a shared purpose: to
            serve our community with integrity, professionalism, and care.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We set our highest goal to hire only the safest and most trusted
            individuals, so that every ride home feels personal, secure, and
            reliable. With Chasers, you're not relying on a faceless app—you're
            trusting a real person, with a real commitment to getting you and
            your vehicle home safely.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We believe that when one of us succeeds, we all succeed. That's why
            our culture is rooted in teamwork and service—both to our members
            and to one another. Together, we make sure every client gets home
            safely, and every experience reflects the standard of excellence
            Chasers is known for.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#c69214] font-serif">
            One mission. One team. One call at a time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Contact Form -->
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-800 to-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700"
        >
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-serif">
            Get in Touch
          </h2>

          <form
            action="https://formspree.io/f/moqrplda"
            method="POST"
            class="space-y-6"
          >
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label
                  for="firstName"
                  class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2"
                >
                  First Name *
                </label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="firstName"
                  name="firstName"
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:border-[#c69214] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#c69214] focus:outline-none transition-colors"
                  placeholder="Enter your first name"
                />
              </div>

              <div>
                <label
                  for="lastName"
                  class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2"
                >
                  Last Name *
                </label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="lastName"
                  name="lastName"
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:border-[#c69214] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#c69214] focus:outline-none transition-colors"
                  placeholder="Enter your last name"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label
                for="email"
                class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2"
              >
                Email Address *
              </label>
              <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                name="email"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:border-[#c69214] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#c69214] focus:outline-none transition-colors"
                placeholder="your.email@example.com"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label
                for="phone"
                class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2"
              >
                Phone Number
              </label>
              <input
                type="tel"
                id="phone"
                name="phone"
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:border-[#c69214] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#c69214] focus:outline-none transition-colors"
                placeholder="(555) 123-4567"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label
                for="serviceType"
                class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2"
              >
                Service Interest
              </label>
              <select
                id="serviceType"
                name="serviceType"
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white focus:border-[#c69214] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#c69214] focus:outline-none transition-colors"
              >
                <option value="">Select service type</option>
                <option value="standard-individual"
                  >Standard Individual ($59.99/month)</option
                >
                <option value="individual"
                  >Individual Premier ($89.99/month)</option
                >
                <option value="joint">Joint Plan ($89.99/month)</option>
                <option value="joint-premier"
                  >Joint Premier ($149.99/month)</option
                >
                <option value="family">Friends & Family ($249.99/month)</option>
                <option value="business">Business Plan ($599.99/month)</option>
                <option value="business-premier"
                  >Business Premier ($699.99/month)</option
                >
                <option value="chauffeur">Chauffeur Services</option>
                <option value="luxury-transport">Luxury Transportation</option>
                <option value="car-concierge">Car Concierge Services</option>
                <option value="gift-membership">Gift Membership</option>
                <option value="other">Other Inquiry</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label
                for="message"
                class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-300 mb-2"
              >
                Message *
              </label>
              <textarea
                id="message"
                name="message"
                rows="5"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:border-[#c69214] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#c69214] focus:outline-none transition-colors resize-vertical"
                placeholder="Tell us about your transportation needs..."
              ></textarea>
            </div>

            <button
              type="submit"
              class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#c69214] to-[#b8841c] text-black py-4 px-6 rounded-xl font-bold hover:from-[#b8841c] hover:to-[#a67619] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105"
            >
              Send Message
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Direct Contact -->
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-800 to-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700"
          >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-serif">
              Get in Touch
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div
                  class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#c69214] to-[#b8841c] w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6 text-black"
                    fill="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  >
                    <path
                      d="M2 3a1 1 0 011-1h2.153a1 1 0 01.986.836l.74 4.435a1 1 0 01-.54 1.06l-1.548.773a11.037 11.037 0 006.105 6.105l.774-1.548a1 1 0 011.059-.54l4.435.74a1 1 0 01.836.986V17a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2C7.82 18 2 12.18 2 5V3z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1">Phone</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">
                    Available 24/7 for your convenience
                  </p>
                  <a
                    href="tel:+14806953659"
                    class="text-[#c69214] hover:text-[#b8841c] font-medium"
                  >
                    (480) 695-3659
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div
                  class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#c69214] to-[#b8841c] w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6 text-black"
                    fill="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  >
                    <path
                      d="M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z"
                    ></path>
                    <path
                      d="M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1">Email</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">
                    Multiple departments for specialized service
                  </p>
                  <div class="space-y-1">
                    <a
                      href="mailto:memberships@chasersdd.com"
                      class="text-[#c69214] hover:text-[#b8841c] font-medium block"
                      >memberships@chasersdd.com</a
                    >
                    <a
                      href="mailto:drivers@chasersdd.com"
                      class="text-[#c69214] hover:text-[#b8841c] font-medium block"
                      >drivers@chasersdd.com</a
                    >
                    <a
                      href="mailto:carconcierge@chasersdd.com"
                      class="text-[#c69214] hover:text-[#b8841c] font-medium block"
                      >carconcierge@chasersdd.com</a
                    >
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div
                  class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#c69214] to-[#b8841c] w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6 text-black"
                    fill="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  >
                    <path
                      fill-rule="evenodd"
                      d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"
                      clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1">
                    Service Area
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Premium transportation throughout</p>
                  <p class="text-[#c69214] font-medium">Greater Phoenix Area</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Business Hours -->
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-800 to-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700"
          >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-serif">
              Business Hours
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div
                class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-gray-700"
              >
                <span class="text-gray-300">Monday - Friday</span>
                <span class="text-white font-medium">3PM - 3AM</span>
              </div>
              <div
                class="flex justify-between items-center py-2 border-b border-gray-700"
              >
                <span class="text-gray-300">Saturday - Sunday</span>
                <span class="text-white font-medium">3PM - 3AM</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2">
                <span class="text-gray-300">Holidays</span>
                <span class="text-white font-medium"
                  >5PM - 12AM</span
                >
              </div>
            </div>

            <div
              class="mt-6 p-4 bg-[#c69214]/10 rounded-lg border border-[#c69214]/20"
            >
              <p class="text-[#c69214] text-sm font-medium">
                ✨ Premium evening transportation when you need it most
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Quick Actions -->
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-800 to-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700"
          >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-serif">
              Quick Actions
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div
                class="relative block w-full bg-gray-400 text-gray-600 py-3 px-6 rounded-xl font-bold cursor-not-allowed opacity-75 text-center group"
              >
                View Membership Plans
                <div
                  class="absolute -top-12 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 bg-gray-800 text-white text-sm px-3 py-2 rounded-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-200 whitespace-nowrap z-10"
                >
                  Please call (480) 695-3659 to sign up
                </div>
              </div>
              <a
                href="/how-it-works"
                class="block w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700 to-gray-800 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-xl font-bold hover:from-[#c69214] hover:to-[#b8841c] hover:text-black transition-all duration-300 text-center"
              >
                Learn How It Works
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  // Form submission handling
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
    const form = document.querySelector("form");
    if (form) {
      form.addEventListener("submit", function (e) {
        const submitButton = form.querySelector('button[type="submit"]');
        const originalText = submitButton.textContent;

        submitButton.textContent = "Sending...";
        submitButton.disabled = true;

        // Reset button after 3 seconds if form doesn't redirect
        setTimeout(() => {
          submitButton.textContent = originalText;
          submitButton.disabled = false;
        }, 3000);
      });
    }
  });
</script>
